 Oba Idowu Abiodun Oniru, the Oniru of Iruland has passed on, The Nation is reporting. The 82-year-old king died today, although there has been no official confirmation from his children and palace officials. According to Yoruba culture, the death of a monarch is not always announced until after traditional rites are performed. Oba Oniru is the father of media personality Toolz Oniru-Demuren. The post The Nation News: Oba Abiodun Idowu Oniru Passes On appeared first on BellaNaija â€“ Showcasing Africa to the world. Read today!. Source: Bella Naija